There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, orange
1. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |
| Food        | pumpkin | blueberry  |
| Sport       | surfing | volleyball |
| Color   | mauve    | orange |

