.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, coach
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, board-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Job           | coach     | chef |
| Hobby   | board-games | cooking  |
| Transport     | ship      | boat |

