.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-12::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, thai
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, van
1. the dannemann-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | thai     | german   |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | dannemann |
| Transport     | car      | van      |

