There 2 different types of food: cranberry, nectarine
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Birthday      | march        | november  |
| Food          | cranberry  | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | romance   |

