.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, techno
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, roller
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | november | december |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | techno  |
| Transport     | roller | boat    |

 